+
+### Source Code (repository root)
+
+```text
+app/
+в”њв”Ђв”Ђ controllers/
+в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ course-history-controller.js
+в”њв”Ђв”Ђ models/
+в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ student-model.js
+в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ course-history-model.js
+в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ authorization-audit-model.js
+в””в”Ђв”Ђ views/
+    в””в”Ђв”Ђ course-history/
+        в”њв”Ђв”Ђ course-history-page.html
+        в”њв”Ђв”Ђ course-history-empty.html
+        в”њв”Ђв”Ђ course-history-error.html
