 ### Session 2026-03-11
 
 - Q: What records count as course history for this feature? в†’ A: All past enrollments with final outcomes.
 - Q: How should the system behave when a student has no course history yet? в†’ A: Show a dedicated no course history yet message and no course rows.
+- Q: What information must a course history view show? в†’ A: Show academic period, course code, course title, and final outcome for each record, plus grade label and credit value when available.
+- Q: How should total record-source unavailability be handled? в†’ A: Show a distinct unavailable-state message, not an empty-history or partial-history state.
