+
+Add a student-facing constraints editor that lets authenticated students create, update, confirm conflicting, and delete term-specific scheduling constraints used by schedule generation. The implementation will use the repositoryвЂ™s required HTML/CSS/JavaScript plus SQLite stack, with MVC separation between controller flows, persisted constraint models, and view rendering for create/save/delete/error states.
