+- [ ] CHK013 Are rename requirements consistent with duplicate-name validation and overwrite policy rules? [Consistency, Spec В§FR-009]
+- [ ] CHK014 Do the term-scoping requirements align across save, list, rename, delete, and reuse flows? [Consistency, Spec В§FR-002, Spec В§FR-008]
+
+## Acceptance Criteria Quality
+
