+- [ ] CHK016 Are the acceptance scenarios sufficient to distinguish rejection, overwrite confirmation, and successful overwrite as separate outcomes? [Acceptance Criteria, Spec В§US2]
+- [ ] CHK017 Is the rename/delete success criterion measurable enough to verify both list updates and storage consistency after reload? [Measurability, Spec В§SC-004]
